{"tid":391642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳中大前會長周竪峰指罵支那人","createTime":"2017-09-08T02:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T03:34:12.000Z","uid":5195,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7eed4c9ef176928b8393257eae2c7b347c5e8f4","tid":391642,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"去年青年新政游蕙禎和梁頌恆在立法會以英文宣誓時，把「China（中國）」讀成「支那」，引發辱華風波，遭市民炮轟。繼游梁二人後，網絡上流出數段影片，疑似是中文大學學生會前會長周竪峰，向一名廣東話發音不正的人士指罵，大鬧對方為「支那人」。<br />\n<br />\n從影片中所見，有一身穿黑衣、戴眼鏡的男子，情緒激動地向着一名拿着手機、廣東話發音不正的人士大罵，指「講廣東話呀，支那人！講廣東話丫！香港地方你唔X講廣東話！」而該名疑似被罵的男子，更一度以普通話向朋友表示要求報警。"},{"pid":"01aee833527c1c9fa219bf1a7c10f994ee5507dc","tid":391642,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果我夠膽我都會咁做"},{"pid":"8dbf117e1af357429e77869b6252173c3ede3d2a","tid":391642,"uid":29473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:46:27.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708518680f2c5295015cc384c7190538c8e870fd","tid":391642,"uid":74244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0fadeb70533c751ebb7d900f14e61d935e91a6","tid":391642,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:09:00.000Z","msg":"跟本班港豬自己攞來就班支那人講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ea6b49bfa3be0484116c64669fd375f4ca1a4b","tid":391642,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:10:17.000Z","msg":"又犯咩法?"},{"pid":"4d80359933a797a6c4e3c016b880ff165dc7cf01","tid":391642,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:14:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38866f5cb6dbc6fc612